    <item>
      <title>英国市政厅在破产警告后获得 6 亿英镑的资助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/uk-town-halls-get-600-million-boost-after-bankruptcy-warnings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心一波地方当局即将破产，英国政府向英国议会提供了 6 亿英镑（7.65 亿美元）的下一财年预算补充。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/uk-town-halls-get-600-million-boost-after-bankruptcy-warnings</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 15:59:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利 Meloni 与 Stellantis 就汽车生产展开斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/italy-s-meloni-picks-fight-with-stellantis-over-car-production</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼 (Giorgia Meloni) 批评 Stellantis NV 在汽车行业正努力转向电气化之际，将汽车生产转移到成本较低的国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/italy-s-meloni-picks-fight-with-stellantis-over-car-production</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 14:49:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱沙尼亚称北约低估了俄罗斯的战争机器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/russian-ability-to-sustain-war-was-underestimated-says-general</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱沙尼亚最高军事指挥官表示，有关俄罗斯生产弹药和招募部队能力的最新情报促使北约盟国重新评估，并发出一系列警告，为长期冲突做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/russian-ability-to-sustain-war-was-underestimated-says-general</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 13:55:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿拉伯准备开设酒类商店，但仅限外交官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/alcohol-ban-saudi-arabia-opens-first-liquor-shop-signals-loosening-view</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着社会限制的不断放松，沙特阿拉伯即将开设数十年来的第一家酒类商店，但酒精只会出售给外交官。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/alcohol-ban-saudi-arabia-opens-first-liquor-shop-signals-loosening-view</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 13:46:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国通过放宽贷款使用加大对开发商融资的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/china-beefs-up-support-for-developer-funding-by-easing-loan-uses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国监管机构通过扩大获得部分商业贷款的渠道，为陷入困境的开发商提供更多财政支持，这是在股市暴跌之际遏制房地产放缓和重振市场信心的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/china-beefs-up-support-for-developer-funding-by-easing-loan-uses</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 13:12:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧尔班因过度参与而拒绝瑞典加入北约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/orban-set-to-fold-on-sweden-s-nato-bid-after-overplaying-hand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·欧尔班正在准备让他的议员批准瑞典加入北约，此前土耳其议会的批准实际上使布达佩斯成为唯一拒绝军事联盟扩大的国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/orban-set-to-fold-on-sweden-s-nato-bid-after-overplaying-hand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 11:20:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
